cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.PL 

This paper discusses the use of a Neuro-Fuzzy technique for improving software effort estimation, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The use of neural networks and fuzzy logic also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The focus on improving cost estimation and reflecting industry trends suggests a connection to systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the use of Function Point analysis suggests a connection to programming languages (cs.PL).
